description:
On today’s show, Emily’s talking about the most important sexercise you’re not doing yet, and helping you have the healthiest relationships possible.

Emily is joined by Amy Bomberg from In Control, the makers behind the Intensity by Pour Moi, to talk about the significant benefits of pelvic floor health. Plus, she gives her top advice on how to move forward when you’re evolving sexually and your partner’s stuck in the past, the best ways to tease and stimulate ALL the male erogenous zones, and how to recognize when you’re in toxic a friends-with-benefits situation and ways to get out of it.

Thank you for supporting our sponsors who help keep the show FREE: Intensity, Adam & Eve, JO Jellies, Magic Wand
